Package edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.IF.expr Description

The public interface package dealing with symbolic expressions. SymbolicExpression defines the interface for a symbolic expression, the root of the symbolic expression type hierarchy. Two sub-types are BooleanExpression (used for all expressions of boolean type) and NumericExpression (used for all expressions with a numeric type).
